ray-400\">A world where quality education is available to everyone, everywhere</p></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-white\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2\">Our Values</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Quality, Accessibility, Community, and Innovation in education</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\"><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold font-space-grotesk mb-6\">Our Story</h2><p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-4\">ReSta was born from a simple observation: quality education materials are often locked behind paywalls, making them inaccessible to many students who need them the most.</p><p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-4\">We started in 2024 with a mission to democratize education by providing free, high-quality study materials to students worldwide. Our platform brings together educators, students, and institutions to create a collaborative learning ecosystem.</p><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Today, we serve thousands of students across the globe, helping them achieve their academic and career goals without financial barriers.</p></div><div class=\"glass rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Why Choose ReSta?</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-gray-400\"><li class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full\"></div><span>100% Free - No hidden costs, no subscriptions</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full\"></div><span>Quality Verified - All materials reviewed by experts</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full\"></div><span>Diverse Categories - From school level to competitive exams</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full\"></div><span>Community Driven - Upload and share your own materials</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full\"></div><span>Always Accessible - Available 24/7 on any device</span></li></ul></div></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"col-span-1 md:col-span-2\"><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-white\"><path d=\"M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z\"></path><path d=\"M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold font-space-grotesk gradient-text\">ReSta</span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-4 max-w-md\">Your ultimate destination for free study materials, resources, and educational content. Empowering students and learners worldwide with quality educational resources.</p><div class=\"flex space-x-4\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M15 22